question: How can I apply for admission?
answer: Applying for admission to Collegewala is quite straightforward! You can either apply online or in person. To apply online, just visit our website at www.collegewala.edu, fill out the online application form with your details, upload your required documents like mark sheets and ID proof, pay the application fee, and then submit your form. You will receive the merit list within two weeks, and if you're selected, you can complete your admission at our office. If you prefer to apply in person, you can visit our college office during office hours, which are Monday to Friday, from 9 AM to 5 PM.
